title: The Lost Element
content: The people knew it was time to rise and take the Lost Element from their rulers

title: The Big Cheese
content: Landing on the planet, they were shocked to find that it was in fact made of cheese.

title: The Fragile Bear
content: Cheese was guarded by Bears. One took a liking to an alien.

title: The Angry Mole
content: Bears and Moles fought for the cheese. The alien tried to make a truce.

title: The Banquet
content: Everyone ate cheese together. The aliens were award a big Cheddar Wheel.
